8 mama saha dṛṣṭim, ṛju tena deśena
9 yatra ekaḥ ca gatiḥ anyā ca gatiḥ abhighātam āgacchati;

16 Yadyadi teṣām mārgaḥ na vikṛtaḥ syāt,
17 bahu śubham svarge niṣphalaṃ syāt,
18 tataḥ sarvā api śaktayaḥ adhastāt niṣkriyāḥ syuḥ;

25 Prakṣiptaṃ tvayā puras tasya bhuṅkṣva;
26 mama hi sarvāpi pravṛttiḥ
27 tadviṣaye vartate yataḥ aham lekhakaḥ kṛtaḥ.

31 tenaabhāgenaḥpūrvamasmṛtena
32 yuktaḥ, parivartate sma parivṛttiṣu
33 yāsvayamuttamaḥsadāprakāśate;

43 Atas tatra buddhim kalām prayogam ca āhvayāmi,
44 tathā vakṣyāmi yathā na kadācit kalpitam api syāt;
45 tathāpi viśvasitum śakyate, darśanam ca tasya icchitum arhati.

46 Api ca yadi asmākaṃ kalpanāḥ nīcāḥ santi
47 etāvatyāṃ paramaparvatasya unnatatāyām, na āścaryam;
48 yataḥ sūryasya upari na kaścit akṣiḥ gataḥ asti.

58 yathā aham abhūvam teṣu vacaneṣu;
59 evam ca sarvaḥ mama premaḥ tasminn eva niyuktaḥ abhūt,
60 yataḥ Bēatrice viṣamayām viṣmṛtau.

70 Svargasya sabhāyām yata āgato 'ham,
71 Tatra santi sukhani bahūni priyāṇi ca sundarāṇi ca,
72 Yāny etasmin loke na śakyante ānayitum;

73 Teshām sukhanām eva tat tejomayānām gītam āsīt;
74 Yaḥ puruṣaḥ pakṣau na vardhayati yena sa upari gantum śaknuvāt,
75 Saḥ puruṣaḥ adhastāt eva tad-viṣayam śṛṇuyāt.

85 Tvattaḥpracuratayāprakāśate,
86 Yena tvāṃtāṃśreṇīṃpraṇayasi
87 Yataḥpunarārohaṇamṛteko'pi tiṣṭhati;

